> <span begin="3.492" end="3.848">war</span> <span begin="3.848" end="4.035">with</span> <span begin="4.035" end="4.456">England</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">法国正处于与英国开战的边缘</span></p><p begin="4.862" end="7.679" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4.862" end="5.027">Now,</span> <span begin="5.027" end="5.207">do</span> <span begin="5.207" end="5.427">we</span> <span begin="5.427" end="5.814">provide</span> <span begin="5.814" end="6.123">aid</span> <span begin="6.123" end="6.224">and</span> <span begin="6.224" end="6.613">troops</span> <span begin="6.613" end="6.771">to</span> <span begin="6.771" end="6.891">our</span> <span begin="6.891" end="7.237">French</span> <span begin="7.237" end="7.679">allies</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那么，我们是否要向法国盟友提供援助和兵力</span></p><p begin="7.689" end="9.140" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="7.689" end="7.825">Or</span> <span begin="7.825" end="8.009">do</span> <span begin="8.009" end="8.141">we</span> <span begin="8.141" end="8.534">stay</span> <span begin="8.534" end="8.754">out</span> <span begin="8.754" end="8.897">of</span> <span begin="8.897" end="9.140">it?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">还是说我们置身事外？</span></p><p begin="9.427" end="11.402" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="9.427" end="9.939">Remember,</span> <span begin="10.184" end="10.380">my</span> <span begin="10.380" end="10.815">decision</span> <span begin="10.815" end="10.951">on</span> <span begin="10.951" end="11.115">this</span> <span begin="11.115" end="11.402">matter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">请记住，我对这一事项的决定</span></p><p begin="11.412" end="13.755" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="11.412" end="11.692">Is</span> <span begin="11.692" end="11.959">not</span> <span begin="11.959" end="12.357">subject</span> <span begin="12.357" end="12.457">to</span> <span begin="12.457" end="13.161">congressional</span> <span begin="13.161" end="13.755">approval</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无需经过国会批准</span></p><p begin="13.914" end="16.102" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="13.914" end="14.092">The</span> <span begin="14.092" end="14.366">only</span> <span begin="14.366" end="14.616">person</span> <span begin="14.616" end="14.733">you</span> <span begin="14.733" end="14.833">have</span> <span begin="14.833" end="14.933">to</span> <span begin="14.933" end="15.573">convince</span> <span begin="15.714" end="15.859">is</span> <span begin="15.859" end="16.102">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你们唯一需要说服的人就是我</span></p><p begin="16.305" end="18.558" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.305" end="16.882">Secretary</span> <span begin="16.882" end="17.412">Jefferson,</span> <span begin="17.632" end="17.732">you</span> <span begin="17.732" end="17.832">have</span> <span begin="17.832" end="17.932">the</span> <span begin="17.932" end="18.262">floor,</span> <span begin="18.262" end="18.558">sir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">杰斐逊部长，请发言，先生</span></p><p begin="19.247" end="21.479" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="19.247" end="19.515">When</span> <span begin="19.515" end="19.687">we</span> <span begin="19.687" end="19.868">were</span> <span begin="19.868" end="20.056">on</span> <span begin="20.056" end="20.383">death&apos;s</span> <span begin="20.383" end="20.663">door,</span> <span begin="20.663" end="20.818">when</span> <span begin="20.818" end="20.984">we</span> <span begin="20.984" end="21.163">were</span> <span begin="21.163" end="21.479">needy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我们徘徊在死亡边缘、穷困潦倒之时</span></p><p begin="21.719" end="24.015" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="21.719" end="21.926">We</span> <span begin="21.926" end="22.083">made</span> <span begin="22.083" end="22.207">a</span> <span begin="22.207" end="22.814">promise,</span> <span begin="22.961" end="23.091">we</span> <span begin="23.091" end="23.434">signed</span> <span begin="23.434" end="23.592">a</span> <span begin="23.592" end="24.015">treaty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们许下了诺言，签署了条约</span></p><p begin="24.120" end="26.294" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="24.120" end="24.391">We</span> <span begin="24.391" end="24.581">needed</span> <span begin="24.581" end="24.888">money</span> <span begin="24.888" end="25.043">and</span> <span begin="25.043" end="25.396">guns</span> <span begin="25.396" end="25.496">and</span> <span begin="25.496" end="25.737">half</span> <span begin="25.737" end="25.864">a</span> <span begin="25.864" end="26.294">chance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当时我们需要钱、需要枪，哪怕只有一线生机</span></p><p begin="26.304" end="28.277" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="26.304" end="26.735">Uh,</span> <span begin="26.735" end="26.884">who</span> <span begin="26.884" end="27.378">provided</span> <span begin="27.378" end="27.664">those</span> <span begin="27.664" end="28.277">funds?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">额，是谁提供了那些资金？</span></p><p begin="28.400" end="28.766" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="28.400" end="28.766">France</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是法国</span></p><p begin="29.017" end="31.063" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="29.017" end="29.241">In</span> <span begin="29.241" end="29.711">return,</span> <span begin="29.711" end="29.923">they</span> <span begin="29.923" end="30.303">didn&apos;t</span> <span begin="30.303" end="30.543">ask</span> <span begin="30.543" end="30.680">for</span> <span begin="30.680" end="31.063">land</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">作为回报，他们并没索要土地</span></p><p begin="31.294" end="33.283" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="31.294" end="31.723">Only</span> <span begin="31.723" end="31.823">a</span> <span begin="31.823" end="32.218">promise</span> <span begin="32.218" end="32.320">that</span> <span begin="32.320" end="32.565">we&apos;d</span> <span begin="32.565" end="32.878">lend</span> <span begin="32.878" end="33.009">a</span> <span begin="33.009" end="33.283">hand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仅仅要一个我们会伸出援手的承诺</span></p><p begin="33.293" end="35.754" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="33.293" end="33.393">And</span> <span begin="33.393" end="33.721">stand</span> <span begin="33.721" end="33.882">with</span> <span begin="33.882" end="34.162">them</span> <span begin="34.162" end="34.382">if</span> <span begin="34.382" end="34.649">they</span> <span begin="34.649" end="34.959">fought</span> <span begin="34.959" end="35.274">against</span> <span begin="35.274" end="35.754">oppressors</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">承诺当他们反抗压迫者时，我们会并肩作战</span></p><p begin="35.764" end="38.110" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="35.764" end="35.898">And</span> <span begin="35.898" end="36.477">revolution</span> <span begin="36.477" end="36.611">is</span> <span begin="36.611" end="36.921">messy,</span> <span begin="36.921" end="37.082">but</span> <span begin="37.082" end="37.276">now</span> <span begin="37.276" end="37.385">is</span> <span begin="37.385" end="37.522">the</span> <span begin="37.522" end="37.707">time</span> <span begin="37.707" end="37.807">to</span> <span begin="37.807" end="38.110">stand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">革命确实是混乱的，但现在是挺身而出的时刻了</span></p><p begin="38.346" end="40.781" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="38.346" end="38.713">Stand</span> <span begin="38.713" end="38.851">with</span> <span begin="38.851" end="38.992">our</span> <span begin="38.992" end="39.346">brothers</span> <span begin="39.346" end="39.455">as</span> <span begin="39.455" end="39.555">they</span> <span begin="39.555" end="39.897">fight</span> <span begin="39.897" end="40.202">against</span> <span begin="40.202" end="40.781">tyranny</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">与我们的兄弟们站在一起，对抗暴政</span></p><p begin="40.880" end="42.814" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="40.880" end="41.070">I</span> <span begin="41.070" end="41.322">know</span> <span begin="41.322" end="41.422">that</span> <span begin="41.422" end="42.028">Alexander</span> <span begin="42.028" end="42.486">Hamilton</span> <span begin="42.486" end="42.647">is</span> <span begin="42.647" end="42.814">here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道亚历山大·汉密尔顿就在这儿</span></p><p begin="42.830" end="44.804" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="42.830" end="42.961">And</span> <span begin="42.961" end="43.092">he</span> <span begin="43.092" end="43.240">would</span> <span begin="43.240" end="43.520">rather</span> <span begin="43.520" end="43.818">not</span> <span begin="43.818" end="44.133">have</span> <span begin="44.133" end="44.347">this</span> <span begin="44.347" end="44.804">debate</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他宁愿不要进行这场辩论</span></p><p begin="44.904" end="47.905" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="44.904" end="45.170">I</span> <span begin="45.170" end="45.656">remind</span> <span begin="45.656" end="45.913">you</span> <span begin="45.913" end="46.122">that</span> <span begin="46.122" end="46.290">he</span> <span begin="46.290" end="46.501">is</span> <span begin="46.501" end="46.710">not</span> <span begin="46.710" end="47.297">Secretary</span> <span begin="47.297" end="47.431">of</span> <span begin="47.431" end="47.905">State</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我得提醒你，他并不是国务卿</span></p><p begin="48.163" end="50.230" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="48.163" end="48.347">He</span> <span begin="48.347" end="48.620">knows</span> <span begin="48.620" end="49.018">nothing</span> <span begin="49.018" end="49.138">of</span> <span begin="49.138" end="49.791">loyalty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他对忠诚一无所知</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="49.791" end="50.230"><span begin="49.791" end="50.230">(Nothing)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一窍不通</span></span></p><p begin="50.240" end="52.783" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="50.240" end="50.567">Smells</span> <span begin="50.567" end="50.835">like</span> <span begin="50.835" end="51.049">new</span> <span begin="51.049" end="51.394">money,</span> <span begin="51.394" end="51.775">dresses</span> <span begin="51.775" end="52.084">like</span> <span begin="52.084" end="52.352">fake</span> <span begin="52.352" end="52.783">royalty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">闻起来像个暴发户，穿得像个假王室</span></p><p begin="52.785" end="54.525" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="52.785" end="53.349">Desperate</span> <span begin="53.349" end="53.449">to</span> <span begin="53.449" end="53.725">rise</span> <span begin="53.725" end="53.951">above</span> <span begin="53.951" end="54.058">his</span> <span begin="54.058" end="54.525">station</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">拼了命想爬出他那卑微的出身</span></p><p begin="54.847" end="57.584" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="54.847" end="55.341">Everything</span> <span begin="55.341" end="55.545">he</span> <span begin="55.545" end="55.848">does</span> <span begin="55.848" end="56.368">betrays</span> <span begin="56.368" end="56.502">the</span> <span begin="56.502" end="56.955">ideals</span> <span begin="56.955" end="57.055">of</span> <span begin="57.055" end="57.161">our</span> <span begin="57.161" end="57.584">nation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他的一举一动都在背叛我们国家的理想</span></p><p begin="59.019" end="1:02.375" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="59.019" end="59.368">Hey,</span> <span begin="59.572" end="59.691">and</span> <span begin="59.691" end="59.858">if</span> <span begin="59.858" end="59.977">you</span> <span begin="59.977" end="1:00.310">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:00.310" end="1:00.911">know,</span> <span begin="1:00.911" end="1:01.137">now</span> <span